StellarEmporium.Name: Stellar Emporium
StellarEmporium.Description: The ultimate market where intergalactic traders barter rare items from the far reaches of the universe. Beware of wormhole discounts!

GalacticForge.Name: Galactic Forge
GalacticForge.Description: A forge where the most durable and advanced weapons are crafted using the energy of stars.

DimensionalRiftCafe.Name: Dimensional Rift Café
DimensionalRiftCafe.Description: Enjoy snacks from across space and time while watching rifts open to parallel dimensions. Just don’t spill your tea—it could destabilize reality.

TechnomancerSanctuary.Name: Technomancer Sanctuary
TechnomancerSanctuary.Description: A hidden store for those who blend magic and technology. This sanctuary has everything from spell-coded microchips to enchanted hard drives.

AstralOperaHouse.Name: Astral Opera House
AstralOperaHouse.Description: Home to performances that transcend time and space. Witness concerts played on instruments made of stardust, and operas echoing across galaxies.

BlackHoleBazaar.Name: Black Hole Bazaar
BlackHoleBazaar.Description: A mysterious marketplace located at the edge of a black hole. They say the gravity here is as irresistible as the deals.

TimekeepersGuild.Name: Timekeeper's Guild
TimekeepersGuild.Description: A secret guild devoted to preserving and manipulating the flow of time. Rumor has it that guild members can craft devices that bend reality itself.

CelestialFarm.Name: Celestial Farm
CelestialFarm.Description: An advanced farm where crops are grown in zero gravity using sunlight harvested from distant stars. Its produce is the finest in the cosmos.

QuantumSpa.Name: Quantum Spa
QuantumSpa.Description: Relax as the quantum fields realign your energy and massage away your atomic stress. The spa of the future, where science meets relaxation.

NebulaLibrary.Name: Nebula Library
NebulaLibrary.Description: A library that spans entire star systems. This is where the knowledge of the ancients, travelers, and lost civilizations is stored for curious minds.

VoidCasino.Name: Void Casino
VoidCasino.Description: Test your luck in games where the stakes are as high as the gravity is low. Just don’t bet your ship—or your existence.

HyperNovaResort.Name: HyperNova Resort
HyperNovaResort.Description: A luxury resort for those looking to escape the daily grind of galactic life. The plasma pools are heated by nearby suns!

InfiniteEchoMuse.Name: Infinite Echo Museum
InfiniteEchoMuse.Description: A museum dedicated to the cultures that no longer exist. Walk through echoes of civilizations long gone, or witness interactive art made of pure light.

EventHorizonCafe.Name: Event Horizon Café
EventHorizonCafe.Description: A cozy café on the edge of oblivion, where drinks are strong enough to warp space-time. The perfect spot for interdimensional travelers to unwind.

StarshipWorkshop.Name: Starship Workshop
StarshipWorkshop.Description: The go-to place for starship repair and upgrades. Whether you need a warp drive or a new hull coating, this workshop can handle it.

InterdimensionalEmbassy.Name: Interdimensional Embassy
InterdimensionalEmbassy.Description: The hub of interdimensional diplomacy, where ambassadors from across the multiverse negotiate treaties and share knowledge.

CelestialDiner.Name: Celestial Diner
CelestialDiner.Description: An intergalactic pit stop where you can grab a bite to eat on your way across the stars. The zero-G fries are out of this world!
